---
By: Shantidasa
Source:
  ID: 57c5499b-c3b2-4b09-92a9-a6e977a32050
  Locus:
    Page: 217
    Verse: 9
Tags:
  - Growth
---
Growth cannot be had without first death; gain cannot be realized without a
corresponding loss. Always must opposites occur together, one rises high
that the other might fall.
